      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece of automotive preservation. This vehicle arrives in flawless, showroom-condition, representing the gold standard for pre-owned excellence. Meticulously curated and maintained to an exacting standard, it offers the seamless performance and pristine aesthetics of a brand-new arrival. For the buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that transcends the typical market offerings. Experience the confidence of driving a machine that looks, feels, and performs as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48900.0,
