    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! I\u2019m finally parting with my absolute pride and joy. I have babied this beauty from day one, always keeping it tucked away in the garage and hand-washing it every single weekend. It honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014the paint has that deep, mirror-like shine and the interior still feels crisp and fresh. There is one tiny little mark on the rear rim that you\u2019d honestly miss if I didn't point it out, but otherwise, she\u2019s just about perfect. I\u2019m looking for a fellow car enthusiast who will appreciate her as much as I have. Swing by, let\u2019s have a chat, and I\u2019ll get you the keys for a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a meticulously sorted E46 M3, presented in collector-grade condition. This S54 powerplant delivers visceral linear acceleration all the way to its 8,000 RPM redline, benefiting from a recent comprehensive top-end refresh and precision valve shim adjustment to ensure the individual throttle bodies are perfectly synchronized. The high-pressure VANOS unit has been fully bulletproofed with upgraded seals and rattle kits, while the rear subframe\u2014a critical structural point\u2014has been reinforced with laser-cut plates to ensure a rock-solid chassis under high-torque loads. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides crisp, tactile engagement with zero synchro hesitation. Suspension geometry is optimized via a dialed-in set of adjustable dampers, offering neutral handling and exceptional turn-in bite. This is a turn-key precision instrument maintained to a standard that far exceeds factory specifications. Ready for the canyon or the concours.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    }
